---
layout: base
title: "Speak at nullEDGE 2026 | Call for Proposals"
description: "Share your ServiceNow expertise with folks. Submit your talk for nullEDGE 2026 events."
permalink: /speakers/
---

<div class="container wrapper flow">
  {# Hero Section #}
  <section class="prose text-center">
    <span class="badge">Call for Proposals</span>
    <h1>Speak at nullEDGE 2026</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Share your ServiceNow expertise with folks worldwide. 
      No sales pitches—just real code and actual implementations.
    </p>
    
    <div class="button-group">
      <a href="#events" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary">View Events & Submit</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# Why Speak Section #}
  <section class="region flow">
    <h2 class="text-center">Why Speak at nullEDGE?</h2>
    <div class="grid-3col gap-l">
      <div class="card flow">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <span class="fa-solid fa-users"></span>
        </div>
        <h3>Reach Folks</h3>
        <p>Connect with ServiceNow developers, admins, and architects who are eager to learn from your experience.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card flow">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <span class="fa-solid fa-bullhorn"></span>
        </div>
        <h3>Build Your Brand</h3>
        <p>Establish yourself as a thought leader in the ServiceNow community. All sessions are recorded and promoted.</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card flow">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <span class="fa-solid fa-plane-departure"></span>
        </div>
        <h3>Zero Pressure</h3>
        <p>Virtual format means no travel required. Casual, practitioner-focused environment—be yourself and share what you know.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# What We're Looking For #}
  <section class="region flow">
    <h2 class="text-center">What We're Looking For</h2>
    <div class="card flow">
      <div class="flow gap-m">
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <span class="fa-regular fa-circle-check checklist-icon"></span>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold">Real-World Implementations</p>
            <p class="text-muted">Production code, actual architectures, and lessons learned from live systems</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <span class="fa-regular fa-circle-check checklist-icon"></span>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold">Technical Deep Dives</p>
            <p class="text-muted">Show us the code, walk through the logic, explain the technical decisions</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <span class="fa-regular fa-circle-check checklist-icon"></span>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold">Problem-Solving Stories</p>
            <p class="text-muted">How you solved a tough challenge, what didn't work, and what you'd do differently</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <span class="fa-regular fa-circle-check checklist-icon"></span>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold">Community Contributions</p>
            <p class="text-muted">Open source tools, scripts, frameworks, or methodologies you've built and shared</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="checklist-item">
          <span class="fa-regular fa-circle-check checklist-icon"></span>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold">Practitioner Perspectives</p>
            <p class="text-muted">Your experience in the trenches—what works, what doesn't, and why</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="alert alert-warning">
        <p class="font-semibold">What We DON'T Want:</p>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted">
          Sales presentations, marketing pitches, or theoretical overviews.
          nullEDGE is 100% practitioner-focused—keep it technical and authentic.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# Events with CFP #}
  <section id="events" class="region flow">
    <h2 class="text-center">2026 Events Accepting Proposals</h2>
    
    {% set events2026Sorted = events['2026'] | eventsToArray %}
    {% set cfpEvents = [] %}
    {% for event in events2026Sorted %}
      {% if event.speakerRegistrationUrl %}
        {% set cfpEvents = (cfpEvents.push(event), cfpEvents) %}
      {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
    
    {% if cfpEvents.length > 0 %}
      <div class="grid-2col gap-l">
        {% for event in cfpEvents %}
        <div class="card flow">
          <div class="card-header">
            <div class="flex-between">
              <h3 class="h4">{{ event.name }}</h3>
              <span class="badge">CFP Available</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-muted">{{ event.description }}</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card-body flow gap-s">
            <div class="info-item">
              <span class="fa-regular fa-calendar"></span>
              <span>Event: {{ event.when.start | formatDate("MMMM D, YYYY") }}</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-item">
              <span class="fa-solid fa-presentation-screen"></span>
              <span>
                {% if event.type == 'full-day' %}
                  Seeking {{event.sessionCount}} sessions
                {% elif event.type == 'sessions' %}
                  Seeking {{event.sessionCount}} sessions
                {% elif event.sessionCount > 0 %}
                  {{ event.sessionCount }} sessions planned
                {% else %}
                  Multiple sessions
                {% endif %}
              </span>
            </div>
            
            {% if event.speakerSubmissionStart and event.speakerSubmissionEnd %}
            <div class="info-item">
              <span class="fa-regular fa-clock"></span>
              <span>CFP: {{ event.speakerSubmissionStart | formatDate("MMM D") }} - {{ event.speakerSubmissionEnd | formatDate("MMM D, YYYY") }}</span>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
              </span>
            </div>
            
            {% if event.speakerSubmissionStart and event.speakerSubmissionEnd %}
            <div class="info-item">
              <span class="fa-regular fa-clock" style="font-size:32px;"></span>
              <span>CFP: {{ event.speakerSubmissionStart | formatDate("MMM D") }} - {{ event.speakerSubmissionEnd | formatDate("MMM D, YYYY") }}</span>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            
            <a href="{{ event.speakerRegistrationUrl }}" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              Submit Your Talk
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    {% else %}
      <div class="card flow cfp-placeholder">
        <div class="cfp-placeholder-icon">
          <span class="fa-regular fa-calendar-plus"></span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-center">Call for Proposals Opening Soon</h3>
        <p class="text-muted text-center">
          We'll be accepting speaker proposals for our 2026 events starting early next year. 
          Check back in January 2026 or follow us on social media for the announcement.
        </p>
        
        <div class="cfp-timeline">
          <h4>Upcoming CFP Dates</h4>
          <div class="flow gap-s">
            {% for event in events2026Sorted %}
              {% if event.speakerSubmissionStart and event.speakerSubmissionEnd %}
              <div class="cfp-timeline-item">
                <div class="cfp-timeline-header">
                  <span class="font-semibold">{{ event.name }}</span>
                  <span class="badge badge-sm">{{ event.when.start | formatDate("MMM D, YYYY") }}</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-muted">
                  CFP Opens: <strong>{{ event.speakerSubmissionStart | formatDate("MMMM D, YYYY") }}</strong><br>
                  CFP Closes: <strong>{{ event.speakerSubmissionEnd | formatDate("MMMM D, YYYY") }}</strong>
                </p>
              </div>
              {% endif %}
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="button-group">
          <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline">View Event Schedule</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    {% endif %}
  </section>

  {# FAQ Section #}
  <section class="region flow">
    <h2 class="text-center">Speaker FAQ</h2>
    <div class="flow gap-m">
      <div class="card flow">
        <h3 class="h4">How long should my session be?</h3>
        <p class="text-muted">
          Sessions are 15 minutes.  We're looking for concise, focused talks that get to the point quickly.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card flow">
        <h3 class="h4">Do I need to be an expert?</h3>
        <p class="text-muted">
          No! If you've built something interesting, solved a tough problem, or learned valuable lessons, you have something to share. Authenticity matters more than credentials.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card flow">
        <h3 class="h4">Will sessions be recorded?</h3>
        <p class="text-muted">
          Yes, all sessions are recorded and published on our YouTube channel. This helps extend your reach beyond the live event.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="card flow">
        <h3 class="h4">Can I submit multiple proposals?</h3>
        <p class="text-muted">
          Absolutely! Feel free to submit multiple topics. We appreciate speakers with multiple areas of expertise.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {# CTA Section #}
  <section class="region text-center">
    <div class="card flow prose">
      <h2>Ready to Share Your Knowledge?</h2>
      <p>Join 40+ speakers who presented at nullEDGE 2025. The community is waiting to learn from your experience.</p>
      <div class="button-group">
        <a href="#events" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary">Submit Your Talk</a>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-lg btn-outline">View Upcoming Events</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

